d":"edc60c131ad49074bbad1e7b40a17917f369bed9","tid":1772241,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"[食好野] 中國自古就是食人族社會 滅絕人性的中華食人傳統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/517176\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/517176</a><br />\n<br />\n劉仲敬：愛沙尼亞人和烏克蘭人覺得跟斯大林同志比，希特勒已經很仁慈。諸夏各民族有更多的理由認為，跟中國侵略者比起來，蘇聯非常文明。中國人不僅是全世界最大最古老的食人族，而且是全世界唯一不以為恥反以為榮的食人族。阿兹特克人虽然在前一方面跟中国人并驾齐驱，在后一方面却大大落伍。<br />\n<br />\n而且所謂中國人歷史最好睇嘅就係，睇住呢個戇鳩民族周期性人口暴增跟住短時間內大滅絕reset，幾千年嚟無限loop,真係搵唔到其他地方嘅歷史可以有咁精彩"},{"pid":"a95ab8a595cbf8c49a6d307858c5ac9a00e071a6","tid":1772241,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:10:30.000Z","msg":"個post有聲"},{"pid":"c14cc666210c718c18dde04a3bf1176dc59567dc","tid":1772241,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"男嘅都可以俾人屌喎"},{"pid":"d96c56ff559e9f5957978077c3c1b681b103713e","tid":1772241,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14cc666210c718c18dde04a3bf1176dc59567dc","tid":1772241,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"男嘅都可以俾人屌喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"支那幹部啲小農基因出錯，全部都玩得好偏㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339dfe7ba78f96940dda104f642c51b8b43338cd","tid":1772241,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96c56ff559e9f5957978077c3c1b681b103713e","tid":1772241,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c14cc666210c718c18dde04a3bf1176dc59567dc","tid":1772241,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:26.000Z","msg":"男嘅都可以俾人屌喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"支那幹部啲小農基因出錯，全部都玩得好偏㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c